lass=headings><font color=#A0B0E0>Comment</font></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uelcerdodiablo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>El Cerdo Diablo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/21/02 2:50:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13187.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Been away from EQ for a year, need help with gear</span><hr size=1> I've been away from EQ for just short of a year (10-11 months), and I just came back to playing this past week.  I've had many comments (un-asked for) about my gear since I got back.  <br><br>So. . .help me out guys.  I'll list out what I have now, and you can suggest anything that I might be able to track down that would be considered an upgrade.  I mainly could use better stuff in my non-visible slots (waist/ears/face especially).  <br><br>Any item that you suggest as an upgrade has to be either:<br><br>a)  acquireable by a single group.  Nothing off any mob that takes more than one group to kill <br><br>OR<br><br>b)  cheaply purchaseable (under 2k or so).  <br><br>I am no longer in any guild, and I don't plan on joining one, as I cannot play much at all, and guilds tend to complain if you don't come along for raids.  So I do not have a guild to help me get gear either, I have to get it all myself. <br><br><br>Heres what I have now. <br><br>Ear1:  Orc Fang Earring<br>Ear2:  Diamondine Earring<br>Neck:  Ravenscale Neckguard<br>Face:  Dented Brass Mask<br>Head:  Froglok Crown (not changing this, I want a helm with no graphic)<br>Hands:  Woven Shadow Gloves<br>Wrist1:  Hero Bracer<br>Wrist2:  Mrylokar's Bracer<br>Arms:    Mrylokar's <br>Shoulders:  Obulus Mantle <br>Chest:  Woven Shadow Chestguard<br>Waist:  Straw Spun Belt (I know, I know. . .)<br>Back:    Ravenscale Cloak<br>Legs:    Woven Shadow Leggings<br>Feet:    Woven Shadow Boots<br><br>Weap1:  Ragebringer<br>Weap2:  Shadow Rager (which I could swear was nodrop before)<br>Range:  Runed Bone Fork<br><br><br>Cullyn Shadowstalker<br>Barbarian Rogue of the 52.95th Circle<br>Solusek Ro<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usaevanjnoir.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Saevan JNoir</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/21/02 3:46:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13187.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Been away from EQ for a year, need help with gear</span><hr size=1> What the hell's wrong with that equipment? /sigh ... twinks these days (not you, the people commenting).<br><br>Minor upgrades at best are all that I can see based on your cost and accessability requirements. <br><br>Replace the diamondine earring with cougar claw or orc fang. Hope for a sarnak earring of station or better while hunting Chardok.<br><br>Replace the DB mask with a cougarskin mask, an easy quest in Iceclad. <br><br>Replace the RS neck with a spider fur collar.<br><br>Replace the belt with TBB maybe?<br><br>Other then that, look for upgrades on stuff as you are xp hunting, in Sebalis (pick up groups) and Chardok (bring a group) for example.  <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=10371>Saevan J’Noir - Teir'Dal Garden Tool</a><br>Cult of the Ancient Wyrm<br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uhyarth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hyarth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/21/02 3:57:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13187.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Been away from EQ for a year, need help with gear</span><hr size=1> Knowing what level you are would help, but on the whole there is nothing wrong with that gear.  Look into doing the Coldain Rings, those are easily obtainable upgrades (up to the 8/9th that is.)  I suppose you could pick a Velious faction (like dwarves) and spend some time crawling around Kael for some quest armor.  But on the whole, I'd say relax and got <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> expl</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->[/b]  You have the wonderful advantage of not having had everything spoiled left, right, and center for you.  Take advantage of a year's worth of unexplored content and go have some fun. <p><IMG SRC="http://www.personal.psu.edu/~mxd263/eqimage/newsig2.jpg"><BR>Shutup, before I cudgel you to death with this olive branch and unleash my eye-gouging white doves. </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usaevanjnoir.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Saevan JNoir</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/21/02 4:03:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13187.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Been away from EQ for a year, need help with gear</span><hr size=1> He is 52.95, according to his sig. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=10371>Saevan J’Noir - Teir'Dal Garden Tool</a><br>Cult of the Ancient Wyrm<br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=tarasunder>TaraSunder</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/21/02 4:41:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13187.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Been away from EQ for a year, need help with gear</span><hr size=1> hmmm your gear isnt at all bad or anything...but yes there are many upgrades you are able to get solo, grouped and purchased in your budget<br><br>for earrings get a second orc fang for 50pp or less...solo wolves in dawnshroud peaks for a new earring that drops there thats better then the orc fangs(cant remember the name atm though =/)...get in a group in maidens eye to try and get a vah shir claw earring.<br><br>for neck get in a group fighting kobalds in velks for a spider fur collar or quest the dragon tooth choker...only one fight and it can be done with one group(i did it with only a monk, druid and myself).<br><br>for face solo gorehorn in hollowshade moor for his mask or group in seb for gangrenous beetle mask<br><br>for head thats not bad but there are other options for a no graphic helm =P.<br><br>for hands group in velks for crystal chitin gaunts or group in maidens eye for the 25AC rogue/bard guants.<br><br>for wrist group in velks for a silver chitin bracelet...you can also do the ice forged shackle quest with one group or less (think i did that partnered)<br><br>for arms group in velks for crystal chitin arms<br><br>for shoulders depending what faction youre on you can quest the barbed dragonscale pauldrons or buy them(not sure what PC is atm though)<br><br>for chest i dont remember the WS stats atm so i dont know if these are better but you can group in upper dogs in velks for a barbed ringmail or try and get a group in dragon necropolis for a PSC.<br><br>for waist you can solo for a tbb...group in velks fighting kobalds for a spider fur belt or group in maidens eye for axgaroths belt of defense<br><br>for back im not sure if its an upgrade or not but you can also get a spider fur cloak or shimmering terror hide cloak in velks.<br><br>for legs im not quite sure...my legs badly need upgrading lol<br><br>for boots you can get crystal chitin boots in velks<br><br>for ranged you might be able to get some friends to help you camp an idol of the thorned or you can group in maidens eye for a goranga idol or you can solo curfang in hollowshade moor for his heart (keep the RBF for resist gear)<br><br>you can also likely get in a group in kael to get some brigands armor and im sure there are other good choices out there too<br><br>hope that helps (im sure my hunting pattern over my last several lvls is obvious here lol)<br><br>-Tarha Sunderr<br>redeemed and enraged blackguard of tarew marr <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=cosimo>Cosimo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/21/02 5:16:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13187.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Been away from EQ for a year, need help with gear</span><hr size=1> A no graphic helm that I like better for ac/hp gear is a Ry'gorr Chain Coif; it cost me 150pp to get one for my rogue.  <br><br>Stats are 13ac, +3 str, +15 mana, +3 sv magic.  <br><br>Keep the froggy crown if you raid mobs that have fire or cold ae's, sell it otherwise. For everyday use I prefer the Ry'gorr. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=23056>Cosimo Stormcaller</a> - 54 Half Elf Pathfinder<br><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=99300>Cumberbund Roberts</a> - 24 Half Elf Rogue<br>The Rathe server</p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showPrevMessage?topicID=13187.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showNextMessage?topicID=13187.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13187.topic&index=5><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.emailToFriend?topicID=13187.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.threadControl?topicID=13187.topic><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/dagger.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=13187.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=13187.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select n